. *
. * 5. STATIONARITY TESTS
. *
. * 5.1 Augmented Dickey-Fuller test — demand
. * H0: series has a unit root (non-stationary)
. dfuller demand_gwh, regress lags(3)

{txt}Augmented Dickey-Fuller test for unit root         Number of obs   = {res}       80

{txt}{col 32}{hline 10} Interpolated Dickey-Fuller {hline 9}
                  Test         1% Critical       5% Critical      10% Critical
               Statistic           Value             Value             Value
{hline 78}
 Z(t)         {res}    -4.169            -3.538            -2.906            -2.588
{txt}{hline 78}
