{txt}
{com}. *
. * 8. IN-SAMPLE FORECAST ACCURACY (2024 holdout)
. *
. * Predict fitted values over full sample using training model
. predict demand_fitted, dynamic(tm(2024m01)) y
{txt}(13 missing values generated)

{com}. 
. * Compute residuals in test window
. gen residual_test = demand_gwh - demand_fitted if  !train
{txt}(72 missing values generated)

{com}. 
. * Accuracy metrics
. gen abs_err  = abs(residual_test) if  !train
{txt}(72 missing values generated)

{com}. gen sq_err   = residual_test^2    if  !train
{txt}(72 missing values generated)

{com}. gen abs_pct  = abs(residual_test / demand_gwh) * 100 if  !train
{txt}(72 missing values generated)

{com}. 
. summarize abs_err sq_err abs_pct if  !train

{txt}    Variable {c |}        Obs        Mean    Std. Dev.       Min        Max
{hline 13}{c +}{hline 57}
