{txt}{space 5}abs_pct {c |}{res}         12    1.920479     1.36748   .0024417   3.749867
{txt}
{com}. 
. * Compute scalars
. quietly summarize abs_err   if  !train; scalar MAE  = r(mean)
{err}train; invalid name
{txt}{search r(198), local:r(198);}

end of do-file

